      "text": "旅行先は俺の方で考えようと思っているけれど\nもし、希望があったら受け付けるよ",
      "startTime": 11.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2412_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "startTime": 17.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2412_02_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "は……？\nいぇーいっ！\nやった～！",
      "startTime": 22.4000012714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
